"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-2024-04-17-videos-team-usa-basketball-receive-olympic-jerseys\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Team USA men's basketball roster for the upcoming 2024 Paris Olympicswas officially announcedon Wednesday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.741589721592488e-14, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is, predictably, loaded with star power.\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All in all, the team boasts multiple gold medalists, NBA champions, MVPs, and countless All-NBA selections.\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a tremendous collection of talent that will double as one last run at international greatness for older stars like Stephen Curry, LeBron James, Kevin Durant and Anthony Davis.\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 440, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 380, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.170917214822261e-45, \"text\": \"Stephen Curry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\"}, {\"begin\": 395, \"end\": 407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 415, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.525148754074557e-30, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}, {\"begin\": 426, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.002110787021056e-48, \"text\": \"Anthony Davis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To commemorate the momentous accomplishment of earning a spot on the team, each player was hand-delivered the jersey they will be wearing in Paris.\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999983911039, \"rank\": 1.6090524267696841e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Grant Hill, former NBA great and the current managing director of USA Basketball, traveled around the country to knock on doors and present the country's threads.\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.142089946131457e-36, \"text\": \"Grant Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grant_Hill\"}, {\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.290514962426559e-30, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 656, \"end\": 670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9972908366925525, \"rank\": 0.0027165228114267447, \"text\": \"USA Basketball\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is excellent content and a good reminder of how much this means to these players.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Especially the younger ones, like Anthony Edwards, who have never enjoyed this particular roller coaster before.\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 873, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\", \"score\": 0.8852849693611267, \"rank\": 0.1266663796691376, \"text\": \"Anthony Edwards\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Edwards_(actor)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's Bam Adebayo's jersey presentation:  We had to bring some Heat to Paris \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0094\\u00a5Welcome back@Bam1of1!\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8#USABMNTpic.twitter.com/KMCCIHDZ8S  Then there is Jayson Tatum and Jrue Holiday, who made things easy on Hill by playing for the same team up in Boston.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 964, \"end\": 971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1177301522048643e-27, \"text\": \"Adebayo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bam_Adebayo\"}, {\"begin\": 1114, \"end\": 1126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jayson_Tatum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jayson Tatum\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jayson_Tatum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jayson_Tatum\"}, {\"begin\": 1209, \"end\": 1215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.260215298534388e-28, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_Celtics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were teammates once before, back in August 2021 for the Tokyo Olympics where Team USA earned gold yet again.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.741589721592488e-14, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Along for another Olympics!Let us go get another gold@Jrue_Holiday11&@jaytatum0\\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a4\\u009d\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8#USABMNTpic.twitter.com/SxuFhu5rmx  In a fun twist, Hill hid in an office for this next video while waiting for Joel Embiid to walk in.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1535, \"end\": 1546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joel Embiid\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joel_Embiid\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first-time Olympian was thrilled to find Hill there.\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1574, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999998538264769, \"rank\": 1.4617364195571796e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He stays repping the red, white & blue!Welcome to the \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8#USABMNT@JoelEmbiid!pic.twitter.com/IH90pkGU6C  It looks like the Indiana Pacers pulled off a similar operation with Tyrese Haliburton, who will make his own Olympic debut after multiple FIBA appearances.\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1745, \"end\": 1759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.440867815729916e-61, \"text\": \"Indiana Pacers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Pacers\"}, {\"begin\": 1796, \"end\": 1813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyrese_Haliburton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tyrese Haliburton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyrese_Haliburton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyrese_Haliburton\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From Oshkosh to Paris!Let us go to the Olympics,@TyHaliburton22.\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8#USABMNTpic.twitter.com/RS0f94KLSE  Then it was Edwards's turn.\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 2020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's the strongest candidate on the roster to pull off a worthy successor to Vince Carter's dunk of death.\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2098, \"end\": 2110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vince_Carter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vince Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vince_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vince_Carter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic Ant is here \\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0090\\u009cBelieve That@theantedwards_!#USABMNTpic.twitter.com/FAw6G0EiW3  Kevin Durant and Devin Booker made for another easy trip for Hill as teammates on the Phoenix Suns.\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2231, \"end\": 2237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.525148754074557e-30, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}, {\"begin\": 2242, \"end\": 2254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.934329789796009e-48, \"text\": \"Devin Booker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Devin_Booker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both are decorated international athletes as well.\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Suns will be out in Paris.Welcome back to the Olympic stage@KDTrey5&@DevinBook.\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8#USABMNTpic.twitter.com/xKlRF783Sp  For some reason Hill could not make it to the Clippers' facilities in Los Angeles, so coach Ty Lue was given the responsibility of handing over the Olympics jersey to Kawhi Leonard.\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2574, \"end\": 2585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crypto.com_Arena\", \"score\": 0.9999773416000158, \"rank\": 2.2658911597760073e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crypto.com_Arena\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Crypto.com_Arena\"}, {\"begin\": 2599, \"end\": 2602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyronn_Lue\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2229150914960507e-24, \"text\": \"Lue\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyronn_Lue\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tyronn_Lue\"}, {\"begin\": 2671, \"end\": 2684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kawhi_Leonard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kawhi Leonard\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kawhi_Leonard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kawhi_Leonard\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be his first international appearance.\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2734, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have an Olympic team without a Fun Guy.Let\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s get to work, Kawhi!\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8#USABMNTpic.twitter.com/0QYFyDS94I  Finally, it was LeBron and AD's turn.\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2897, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hill FaceTimed in while the pair were in New Orleans with the Los Angeles Lakers for the play-in game against the New Orleans Pelicans.\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 3033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2939, \"end\": 2950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Pelicans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4668532038214673e-18, \"text\": \"New Orleans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Pelicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Pelicans\"}, {\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Lakers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.314235582450839e-63, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Lakers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Lakers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Lakers\"}, {\"begin\": 3012, \"end\": 3032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Pelicans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1986808087050023e-53, \"text\": \"New Orleans Pelicans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Pelicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Pelicans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a Showtime Summer.For the first time since 2012,@KingJames&@AntDavis23will take the court at the Olympics.\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00ba\\u00f0\\u009f\\u0087\\u00b8#USABMNTpic.twitter.com/tvd6C79ntJ  It's always heartwarming to see dreams come true and this was no different.\", \"from\": 3035, \"to\": 3265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What a moment for these 12 men who aim to cement their names in the Olympic record books this summer.\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations  Liam McKeone is a senior writer for the Breaking and Trending News team at Sports Illustrated.\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3554, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3460, \"end\": 3464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Gallagher\", \"score\": 0.9999865945699594, \"rank\": 1.3403882482450993e-05, \"text\": \"Liam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Gallagher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liam_Gallagher\"}, {\"begin\": 3535, \"end\": 3553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.438632502658695e-25, \"text\": \"Sports Illustrated\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_Illustrated\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has been in the industry as a content creator since 2017, and prior to joining SI in May 2024, McKeone worked for NBC Sports Boston and The Big Lead.\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3672, \"end\": 3689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports_Boston\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Sports Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports_Boston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports_Boston\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to his work as a writer, he has hosted the Press Pass Podcast covering sports media and The Big Stream covering pop culture.\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A graduate of Fordham University, he is always up for a good debate and enjoys loudly arguing about sports, rap music, books and video games.\", \"from\": 3845, \"to\": 3986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3859, \"end\": 3877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fordham_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999528522505, \"rank\": 4.709822137829944e-08, \"text\": \"Fordham University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fordham_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fordham_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McKeone has been a member of the National Sports Media Association since 2020.\", \"from\": 3987, \"to\": 4065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4020, \"end\": 4053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Media_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Sports Media Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Media_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Media_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2\\u00a9 2026ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 4067, \"to\": 4144, \"entities\": []}, {\"